===============================================================================

This package contain the codes for reproducing the experiment of "Dynamic Screening: accelerating First-order Algorithms for the Lasso and Group-Lasso." A. Bonnefoy et al.

You can very easily reproduce the 3 experiments of the article on synthetic data and 
corresponding graphics:

1- the screening progression
2- Normalized Running Times and Flops for the Lasso
3- Idem for the Group-Lasso 

Default values corresponds almost to those of the article.

To run experiments from your console just:
$ python -m experiments exp_num 

or for more help
$ python -m experiments -h


For any question feel free to send me an email at:
 antoine.bonnefoy at lif dot univ-mrs dot fr 
